Celebrities and music lovers gathered on Friday in the southern California desert for the beginning of the annual Coachella Valley Music and Arts Festival - the first big arts and music festival of the summer season .
Festival goers danced around in the sun while performers including the headlining act AC/DC was scheduled to take the stage .
